				<div class="text-wrap">
					<h2><a href="http://foreignpolicy.com/2017/04/07/3-questions-trump-must-answer-after-his-syria-strike/">3 Questions Trump Must Answer After His Syria Strike</a></h2>
					<section class="author-meta"><span class="author"><a href="http://foreignpolicy.com/author/peter-feaver" class="author" title="Peter Feaver">Peter Feaver</a></span> | <time class="time" datetime="2017-04-07T11:17:58Z">3 weeks ago</time></section>
